item.title: How You Can Maintain Your Artificial Intelligence Strategies
item.dc:creator: test-envato
item.description: If you’re a company looking to implement AI technology, according to Deloitte’s State of AI in the Enterprise report, enterprise software is the most popular and easiest approach to acquire and develop AI. These systems have access to massive data sets, usually from customers, and can be used by personnel that have little or no AI experience. There will be more software vendors and cloud providers developing AI targeted to specific business operations in the future.
